{
  "stem": "1292.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And towards the end, we was put on a train, you know, those famous trains--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which was locked-- locked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it wasn't very long journey from Krakow to Auschwitz, to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think it's a great distance, but it was very slow in the line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I remember--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a rumor that we're going to Auschwitz, right?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later, I remember, when the train did stop on the sideline, and we have been let out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember there was Jewish prisoners, so maybe the people which did have to help with all this procedure.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they all greeted us with-- they say, from here, is only one way, through the chimney.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They kept on repeating this a few time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a warning?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As information?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As-- as a fact?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did-- we have been in a hurry here and there a little knock.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have been rushed, what they called an [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Be de-liced-- de-liced.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, they was always panicky about this epidemic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wasn't worried about the prisoners, but they was always panicky that-- and we have been-- and then, we did have showers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have been shaven-- everybody was completely shaven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a lot of DDT again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember, I was smothered with that powder.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I suppose you did try to breathe in between, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You did have to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, I remember there was some heap of funny clothes, and everybody tried-- because we was naked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After the shower was no towels or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So everybody did try to grab whatever they can from the heap of clothes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember, because it was late autumn, I think it must have been October--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'44?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember grabbing-- you know the Dutch clogs?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
